     *  Computes  \f$ X \gets \mathrm{op}(A^{-1}) X\f$
     *  @param F field
     * @param X vector of size \p N on a field \p F
     * @param incX stride of \p  X
     * @param A a matrix of leading dimension \p lda and size \p N
